No. 11M5. City of Moundridge, Kansas, et al., Petitioners v. Exxon Mobil Corporation, et al. 565 U.S. 809, 132 S. Ct. 77,

181 L. Ed. 2d 10,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6670. October 3, 2011.

Motion for leave to file a petition for writ of certiorari under seal with redacted copies for the public record granted. Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.

Same case below, 409 Fed. Appx. 362.
